      "date": "2012-08-11 08:59:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e1826c92-e38f-11e1-b6d3-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
